<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$duyan" href="/people/duyan">独眼</a>，<strong title="小说《在无尽无序的汪洋里，紧挨着你》上市了。。想变成有趣的家伙结果却只能有趣而已" class="zu-question-my-bio">小说《在无尽无序的汪洋里，紧挨着你》上…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="42929" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"> 桂林米粉在北京已经建立组织了。<br>沙县小吃由于时间长久模仿者众估计还没形成。但之前福建人有过形成沙县小吃行会并对小吃摊店进行认证的动议。 


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
